    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80b6-97d8-eeaee774693a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Translating analytics into outcomes is a problem that the authors aim to address. For that, the authors focus on developing an interpretable predictive model for student performance. Analisys on data from an undergraduate course shows that there is a relationship betweeen observed study strategies and course-success.",
